{"title":"人民银行调整存款、贷款利率","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":1,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民银行调整存款、贷款利率"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新华社北京电 经国务院批准，银行存款、银行工商贷款、银行农业贷款的利率调整如下："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、银行存款利率"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单位：月息‰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"项 目   现行利率   调整后利率"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单位存款："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1．活期（企业单位）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1．5     1．5"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2．定期（企事业、机关团体）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年     —     3．0"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二年     —     3．6"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年     —     4．2"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城乡居民个人储蓄存款："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1．活期  2．4    2．4"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2．定期"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半年     3．6     3．6"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年     4．5     4．8"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年     5．1     5．7"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年     5．7     6．6"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八年     —     7．5"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华侨人民币储蓄存款："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定期"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年     4．8     5．4"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年     5．4     6．0"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年     6．0     6．9"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、银行工商贷款利率"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单位：月息‰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"项 目 现行利率 调整后利率"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1．流动资金贷款   4．2   6．0"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2．中短期设备和大修理贷款"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年以下（包括一年）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4．2     4．2"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年以上至三年（包括三年）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4．2     4．8"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年以上至五年（包括五年）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4．2     5．4"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3．逾期贷款加收利息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＋20％   ＋20％"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4．挤占挪用银行贷款罚息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＋50％   ＋50％"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说明："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1．工商流动资金贷款利率适用于全民、集体及个体工商业。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2．国营农场办的工商企业、社队办的工商企业，其流动资金贷款和中短期设备贷款，分别按工商企业流动资金和中短期设备贷款的利率办理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、银行农业贷款利率"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单位：月息‰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"项 目 现行利率 调整后利率"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1．国营农业生产费用贷款"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3．6     4．8"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2．国营农业生产设备贷款"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3．6     4．2"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3．社队农业生产费用贷款"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3．6     4．8"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4．社队农业生产设备贷款"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1．8     3．6"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"5．社队企业中的种植业、养殖业生产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"费用贷款 3．6     4．8"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"6．社队企业中的种植业、养殖业生产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"设备贷款 1．8     3．6"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"7．农机专项贷款 1．8     3．6"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"8．预购定金贷款 3．6     4．8"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"9．社员个人贷款 4．2     4．8—6．0"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}